Aira tokens → XRT alembic

The developers’ letter–

Dear Aira tokens holder,

With your help, we have come all the way from the Aira software prototype to the Robonomics platform. Two years of work, more than 50 releases in 6 repositories on GitHub, thousands of commits of the whole group of developers. Your support has led to the emergence of a new technology, which further aims to subdue robots to the Ethereum decentralized computer. You helped it. Thank you!

It is important to understand that this is not the end of the road, but only the very beginning. We have created this new technology, now it needs to grow and also we should train the community to use Robonomics.

The token of the Robonomics platform is called XRT (Robonomics token). You have two options - go through the KYC procedure and wait for the Dutch auction launch, or get the XRT today in 2 steps.

What is the difference between these options for the Aira tokens holder:

Aira → Aira KYC Aira → Aira KYC → XRT
It is always possible to transform Aira KYC into XRT without the developers’ participation, sending the transaction to the alembic Aira KYC → XRT It is not possible to transfer XRT tokens back into Aira KYC
According to the Dutch auction result, 1 Aira KYC can turn into N XRT, but not less than 1:1 If you have taken both steps and got XRT, you cannot count on increasing the number of XRTs.
Aira KYC cannot be used to become a Robonomics provider XRT can be used to secure a quota at the Robonomics lighthouse
Aira KYC cannot be used to pay the commission to the Robonomics providers You can pay for transactions in the Robonomics network with XRT - ETH is not required
Aira KYC is not planned to be used for the Robonomics DAO voting XRT can be used to create offers in the Robonomics DAO about the Dutch auction launch, the change of the team, which manages the ENS record Robonomics.eth
Aira and Aira KYC tokens will not be offered by the developers for dex XRT will be offered by the developers and community to be added to exchanges

To the action!
